-- Florida Region 5 protocols
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'FL5-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'CPR, defibrillation, epinephrine 1mg q3-5min, amiodarone 300mg. Consider sodium bicarbonate for prolonged arrest.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Florida Region 5 - Citrus Sumter Hernando Pasco Pinellas Hillsborough Polk Manatee Hardee Highlands' AND c.state = 'Florida' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'FL5-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'Stroke alert. Cincinnati scale. Last known well. Glucose. Transport to comprehensive stroke center.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Florida Region 5 - Citrus Sumter Hernando Pasco Pinellas Hillsborough Polk Manatee Hardee Highlands' AND c.state = 'Florida' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'FL5-300', 'Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Trauma assessment. Hemorrhage control. C-spine. IV access. Transport to trauma center.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Florida Region 5 - Citrus Sumter Hernando Pasco Pinellas Hillsborough Polk Manatee Hardee Highlands' AND c.state = 'Florida' LIMIT 1;
